name: N286
description: First BRC20 token inscribed on ancient satoshi from block 286. Satoshis numbers from block 286 are known as 'Nakamoto Sats' among Bitcoin researchers. These satoshis are believed to have been minted by Satoshi Nakamoto, the creator of Bitcoin. By acquiring this BRC20 token, you can own a unique piece of Bitcoin history. Additionally, you can explore the BRC20 token named FHAL on satoshi number 392484691617 to discover more about Bitcoin's fascinating past. Get yourself a unique part of Bitcoin history.
